sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / SDK
    participant UI as ml-pipeline-ui<br/>3000/TCP HTTP
    participant API as ml-pipeline (API Server)<br/>8888/TCP HTTP<br/>8887/TCP gRPC
    participant DB as Database<br/>MySQL 3306/TCP<br/>PostgreSQL 5432/TCP
    participant S3 as Object Store<br/>MinIO/S3<br/>9000/TCP or 443/TCP
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Argo as Argo Workflow<br/>Controller
    participant Pods as Pipeline Step Pods<br/>(driver/launcher)
    participant PA as ml-pipeline-persistenceagent
    participant SW as ml-pipeline-scheduledworkflow
    participant Cache as cache-server<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant MW as metadata-writer
    participant MLMD as metadata-grpc-server<br/>8080/TCP gRPC
    participant Envoy as metadata-envoy<br/>9090/TCP gRPC-Web

    Note over User, Pods: Flow 1: Pipeline Submission and Execution
    User->>UI: Browse pipelines<br/>HTTP/3000 (Edge TLS via Route)
    UI->>API: Submit pipeline<br/>HTTP/8888 (Istio mTLS)
    API->>DB: Store pipeline metadata<br/>SQL (Configurable TLS)
    API->>S3: Store pipeline artifacts<br/>S3 API (AccessKey/SecretKey)
    API->>K8s: Create Argo Workflow<br/>HTTPS/443 (SA token)
    K8s->>Argo: Workflow event
    Argo->>Pods: Create step pods<br/>(driver/launcher injected)

    Note over PA, API: Flow 2: Pipeline Status Persistence
    PA->>K8s: Watch Workflows<br/>HTTPS/443 (SA token)
    K8s-->>PA: Workflow status updates
    PA->>API: Report status<br/>gRPC/8887 (Projected SA token)

    Note over SW, K8s: Flow 3: Scheduled Workflow Execution
    SW->>K8s: Watch ScheduledWorkflows<br/>HTTPS/443 (SA token)
    K8s-->>SW: ScheduledWorkflow events
    SW->>K8s: Create Argo Workflows<br/>HTTPS/443 (SA token)

    Note over K8s, Cache: Flow 4: Execution Caching
    K8s->>Cache: Pod CREATE admission<br/>HTTPS/443 (webhook cert)
    Cache->>DB: Check cache<br/>SQL (Username/Password)
    Cache-->>K8s: Allow/modify pod

    Note over MW, Envoy: Flow 5: Metadata Tracking
    MW->>K8s: Watch Workflows<br/>HTTPS/443 (SA token)
    K8s-->>MW: Workflow events
    MW->>MLMD: Write execution metadata<br/>gRPC/8080 (plaintext)
    MLMD->>DB: Store metadata<br/>SQL (Configurable TLS)
    UI->>Envoy: Query metadata<br/>gRPC-Web/9090 (plaintext)
    Envoy->>MLMD: Forward query<br/>gRPC/8080 (plaintext)
    MLMD-->>Envoy: Metadata response
    Envoy-->>UI: gRPC-Web response
